if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('CardDetail')
and name = 'Index_1'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index CardDetail.Index_1
go

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('CardDetail')
and type = 'U')
drop table CardDetail
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: CardDetail */
/*==============================================================*/
create table CardDetail (
ID varchar(50) RowGuidCol not null constraint DF_CardDetail_ID default newid(),
DoNo varchar(50) null,
ClientIP varchar(20) null,
CardID varchar(20) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS not null,
StatusID int null,
CardType int null,
BeginDate datetime null,
EndDate datetime null,
CreateDate datetime not null,
Remark nchar(10) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
EmpID varchar(10) null,
constraint PK_CARDDETAIL primary key nonclustered (ID)
)
ON [PRIMARY]
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'1:换模
2:换料
3:换单
5:机器故障
6:模具故障
4:辅助故障
7:待料
8:无定单
9:其他
10:交班
13:上班
14:下班',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'CardDetail', 'column', 'CardType'
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: Index_1 */
/*==============================================================*/
create clustered index Index_1 on CardDetail (
DoNo ASC
)
go
